high_descs: Turn to the left, go to the cardboard box that is on the floor to the left of the plant.
Pick up the cardboard box from the floor.
Turn around, go left to the chair, hang a right, go to the table that is in front of the couch.
Put the box down on the table.
Go left to the wall, hang a left and go to the end of the table where the TV is.
Pick up the remote control that is on the table.
Hang a left, go forward, hang a right, go to the cardboard box on the table to the left.
Put the remote control in the box that is on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a remote control in a box on a table.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the window on your left.
Pick up the cardboard box on the floor, in front of the window.
Turn around and walk between the TV stand and the coffee table, and turn towards the coffee table at the center of it.
Place the cardboard box on the coffee table.
Turn around and go to the right side of the TV stand.
Pick up the remote control on the front, right corner of the TV stand.
Turn around and go back to the coffee table.
Place the remote control in the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put the remote control in the box on the table.

high_descs: Turn left, turn left again to face the box on the floor.
Pick up the box from the floor.
Walk to the coffee table in the middle of the room.
Put the box down on the coffee table.
Turn left, walk to the door, turn left, turn left again to face the television stand.
Pick up the remote from the television stand.
Turn and walk back to the coffee table.
Put the remote inside of the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: To move a box to the coffee table and put a remote inside of the box.
